{"type":"message","id":"170f1a8f","parentId":"81f4ee35","timestamp":"2026-02-28T20:00:53.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了大量的日志内容。让我深入分析最近 6 小时内的日志（从 2026-02-28 22:00 到 2026-03-01 04:00）。\n\n从日志中我可以看到：\n\n1. **9 个最近 6 小时内的 Session 文件**：\n   - 0db1495e-ad16-44ca-bb65-01a1aba920f8.jsonl\n   - 18f67ba2-d07c-4dd6-ab32-9e760d74b4e3.jsonl\n   - 307f236a-2cff-48d9-babe-ef815a9e99c6.jsonl\n   - 47ba4c99-8801-46c2-8a9d-9efed827fea4.jsonl\n   - 5ac03e0b-3a3a-4765-934b-b6b867bfa9b1.jsonl\n   - 81b00bb7-1101-4cd3-ad66-d6a028791759.jsonl\n   - 8a22704c-09fb-4193-aa62-9c88be7aec83.jsonl\n   - bcecde6f-83a2-46e0-9192-d3c9db20a2e3.jsonl\n   - da18877f-c526-4045-88c9-97bcee626be0.jsonl\n\n2. **从日志中观察到的错误模式**：\n   - Edit 工具精确匹配失败：`\"Could not find the exact text\"` - 多次出现\n   - ENOENT 错误：文件不存在\n   - 429 错误：账户速率限制，频繁出现\n   - Gateway timeout\n\n3. **系统活动**：\n   我注意到系统在持续进行关键维护和优化工作。小说项目的评审正在进行，SWE-Agent-Node 迭代任务频繁执行。同时，EvoMap 服务显示出不稳定性，多个 cron 任务运行，但伴随着大量 429 错误，表明系统面临严重的 API 调用限制。\n\n接下来，我将深入分析这些日志文件，生成详细报告。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我进一步分析错误模式并检查系统资源状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c938e8892b4843348247d4ca","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 深度错误分析\necho \"=== 错误模式统计 ===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -o '\"status\":\"error\"' | wc -l\necho \"error status count\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 429 错误（速率限制）===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -c \"429\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Edit 失败次数 ===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -c \"Could not find the exact text\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== ENOENT 错误次数 ===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -c \"ENOENT\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Gateway 超时次数 ===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -ci \"gateway.*timeout\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== API 错误（500/502/503）===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -cE '\"(500|502|503)\"'\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 子代理相关错误 ===\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone 2>/dev/null | grep -ci \"unknown.*subagent\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dd922e862409467486f3c7eb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 系统资源状态\necho \"=== 磁盘使用 ===\"\ndf -h / | tail -1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 内存使用 ===\"\nfree -m | head -2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== CPU 负载 ===\"\ncat /proc/loadavg\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最近进程 ===\"\nps aux --sort=-%mem | head -6"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d2016917a9a8467383a9ba51","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查最近的 Pattern Registry\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/pattern-registry.md 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":84506,"output":1144,"cacheRead":12480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98130,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772308821425}}
