{"type":"message","id":"2a5d3531","parentId":"a7f73fe5","timestamp":"2026-03-01T00:03:20.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"分析完成，生成了报告，创建了 round 记录，更新了 pattern-registry.md 和每日记忆。现在总结给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 深度日志分析完成 (Round 259)\n\n### 📊 分析统计\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 分析时长 | 6 小时 (02:00 - 08:00) |\n| 日志文件数 | 11 |\n| 健康评分 | **5.8/10** 🟢 |\n\n---\n\n### 🟢 系统显著改善\n\n相比 4 小时前的 Round 258 (04:00)，系统状态**大幅好转**：\n\n| 问题 | Round 258 | Round 259 | 改善 |\n|------|-----------|-----------|------|\n| 429 错误 | 221 | 178 | ⬇️ **-19%** |\n| Gateway 超时 | 73 | 11 | ⬇️ **-85%** |\n| Edit 失败 | 28 | 6 | ⬇️ **-79%** |\n| ENOENT 错误 | 60 | 18 | ⬇️ **-70%** |\n| 子代理错误 | 74 | 20 | ⬇️ **-73%** |\n\n---\n\n### 📈 健康评分趋势\n\n```\nRound 253 (28日 08:00): 8.8/10 ✅\nRound 258 (01日 04:00): 3.5/10 🔴 (429 爆发)\nRound 259 (01日 08:00): 5.8/10 🟢 (+2.3 恢复中)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 仍需关注\n\n1. **429 错误** - 178 次，虽减少但仍较高\n2. **内存使用** - 增加 326 MB，需监控\n3. **Network Error** - 27 次（新增监控）\n\n---\n\n### 📁 生成的报告\n\n- **日志分析**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0800.md`\n- **Round 记录**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-259-20260301-0800/`\n- **Pattern 更新**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/pattern-registry.md`\n- **每日记忆**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-01.md`\n\n---\n\n**结论**: 系统从 04:00 的严重状态（健康评分 3.5）恢复到 5.8，多项错误大幅减少。Gateway 超时从 73 次降至 11 次（-85%），子代理错误从 74 次降至 20 次（-73%）。429 错误虽减少 19% 但仍需关注。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":756,"output":650,"cacheRead":112768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114174,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772323380032}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a56803a","parentId":"2a5d3531","timestamp":"2026-03-01T04:00:01.345Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 1st, 2026 — 12:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772337601337}}
{"type":"message","id":"420e0e81","parentId":"9a56803a","timestamp":"2026-03-01T04:00:27.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行新一轮深度日志分析，时间是 2026-03-01 12:00 PM。需要分析最近 6 小时的日志。\n\n让我执行分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"执行新一轮深度日志分析："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_31711006301f456ab900a5fc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 获取最近 6 小时的日志文件\necho \"=== 最近 6 小时的 Session 日志 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f | sort\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 文件数量和大小 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f | wc -l\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f -exec du -ch {} + 2>/dev/null | tail -1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4d198f58315d45688a3c6e50","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 深度错误分析\necho \"=== 错误模式统计 ===\"\n\necho \"1. error status 数量:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -o '\"status\":\"error\"' | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"2. 429 错误（速率限制）:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -c \"429\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"3. Gateway 超时:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"gateway.*timeout\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"4. Edit 失败:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -c \"Could not find the exact text\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"5. ENOENT 错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -c \"ENOENT\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"6. 子代理错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"unknown.*subagent\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"7. API 500/502/503 错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -cE '\"(500|502|503)\"'\n\necho \"\"\necho \"8. Network Error:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"network.*error\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"9. aborted 错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"aborted\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4be60a35b5404cfdaf49eb6f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 系统资源状态\necho \"=== 系统资源 ===\"\necho \"磁盘:\"\ndf -h / | tail -1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"内存:\"\nfree -m | head -2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"CPU 负载:\"\ncat /proc/loadavg\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Gateway 进程状态 ===\"\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | head -2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":106393,"output":921,"cacheRead":7616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114930,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772337601341}}
