{"type":"compaction","id":"a1d23261","parentId":"8fd70d41","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:05:44.446Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Execute scheduled deep log analysis tasks (\"深度日志分析任务\") for the OpenClaw system\n- Analyze session logs from the last 6 hours for errors, warnings, timeouts, API failures (401/403/429/500), and resource anomalies\n- Generate structured analysis reports with severity-ranked problems (P0/P1/P2/P3)\n- Update evolution history and pattern registry with findings\n- Track system health score trends over time\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Analyze logs from `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`\n- Focus on last 6 hours of data (not just last 30 minutes)\n- Generate reports to `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md`\n- Update evolution-history at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/`\n- Update pattern-registry.md with new patterns\n- Proactively identify issues rather than reporting \"system stable\"\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Round 258 (04:00): Analyzed 9 session log files, identified 429 rate limit crisis (221 occurrences)\n- [x] Round 258: Health score dropped from 8.8 to 3.5 (SEVERE deterioration)\n- [x] Round 258: Generated report `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0400.md`\n- [x] Round 258: Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-258-20260301-0400/`\n- [x] Round 258: Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/pattern-registry.md` with new patterns\n- [x] Round 259 (08:00): Analyzed 11 session log files (5.0 MB)\n- [x] Round 259: Health score improved to 5.8/10 (up from 3.5)\n- [x] Round 259: Generated report `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0800.md`\n- [x] Round 259: Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-259-20260301-0800/`\n- [x] Both rounds: Updated daily memory `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-01.md`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] None - both analysis tasks completed\n\n### Blocked\n- None currently\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **PAT-048 (429 Rate Limit)**: Classified as P0 (emergency) - root cause: multiple cron tasks running in parallel without request throttling\n- **Health Score Methodology**: Calculated based on error frequency reductions between rounds\n- **Trend Analysis**: Implemented comparison between Round 258 vs Round 259 to track improvement\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Continue monitoring 429 errors (reduced from 221 to 178, still elevated)\n2. Next scheduled log analysis at 12:00 (4 hours after Round 259)\n3. Implement API rate limiting (1 second minimum interval between calls) if not done\n4. Consider switching to backup API provider if 429 errors persist\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Health Score Trend**: 8.8 → 3.5 (Round 258) → 5.8 (Round 259) - recovering\n- **Error Pattern Trends**:\n  - PAT-048 (429 rate limiting): 221 → 178 occurrences (improving)\n  - PAT-049 (Gateway timeout): 73 → 11 occurrences (-85% improvement)\n  - PAT-050 (Subagent errors): 74 → 20 occurrences (-73% improvement)\n- **Current System Resources**: Disk 72% (14G available), Memory 64% (1047 MB available), CPU load 0.03\n- **SWE-Agent-Node Status**: 117 total iterations, 74 successful, 302 test cases passing\n- **Key File Paths**:\n  - Pattern Registry: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/pattern-registry.md`\n  - Latest Report: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0800.md`\n  - Daily Memory: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-01.md`\n  - Round History: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- Execute deep log analysis task (cron: evolver-log-analysis) for the OpenClaw system\n- Analyze last 6 hours of session logs at `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`\n- Identify error patterns, performance issues, API failures, configuration issues, and workflow problems\n- Generate report at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md`\n- Update evolution-history at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/`\n- Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns discovered\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Do not just do \"lightweight check\" and say \"system stable\"\n- Proactively dig into potential problems\n- Even without obvious errors, analyze for optimization opportunities\n- Report must include: analysis statistics, issues by severity (P0/P1/P2/P3), detailed info for each issue, concrete improvement suggestions\n- Current time: Sunday, March 1st, 2026 — 12:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Identified 9 session log files from last 6 hours (3.4MB total)\n- [x] Gathered error statistics:\n  - error status: 3\n  - 429 errors (rate limit): 115\n  - Gateway timeout: 16\n  - Edit failures: 8\n  - ENOENT errors: 37\n  - Subagent errors: 28\n  - Network Error: 48\n  - aborted: 19\n- [x] Collected system resource status: 72% disk, 14G available, 1241MB RAM available\n- [x] Confirmed Gateway process running (1022MB memory, PID 2219105)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Analyzing 429 error timing distribution and Network Error details\n- [ ] Counting successful task executions\n- [ ] Identifying most active sessions\n- [ ] Generating the full analysis report\n\n### Blocked\n- None currently\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Analysis scope**: Last 6 hours (360 minutes) of session logs\n- **Error pattern tracking**: Multiple patterns being monitored including PAT-043 through PAT-047 from previous rounds\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Complete detailed error analysis (429 timing, Network Error examples, success counts)\n2. Compare metrics with previous round (Round 259 at 08:00)\n3. Calculate health score and identify trends\n4. Generate report file at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-1200.md`\n5. Create new round directory in evolution-history\n6. Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns found\n\n## Critical Context\n- *