{"type":"message","id":"988ee43a","parentId":"f8543080","timestamp":"2026-03-01T16:00:01.409Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Monday, March 2nd, 2026 — 12:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772380801406}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8ae04db","parentId":"988ee43a","timestamp":"2026-03-01T16:00:31.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行新的深度日志分析任务。当前时间是 2026-03-02 00:00 (午夜)，需要分析最近 6 小时的日志。\n\n让我开始分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"执行新一轮深度日志分析 (Round 263):"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d77c0f778564599b09abe1c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 获取最近 6 小时的日志文件\necho \"=== 最近 6 小时的 Session 日志 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f | sort\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 文件数量和大小 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f | wc -l\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f -exec du -ch {} + 2>/dev/null | tail -1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aa88726e18864bcc81c6b3fe","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 深度错误分析\necho \"=== 错误模式统计 ===\"\n\necho \"1. error status 数量:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -o '\"status\":\"error\"' | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"2. 429 错误（速率限制）:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -c \"429\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"3. Gateway 超时:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"gateway.*timeout\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"4. Edit 失败:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -c \"Could not find the exact text\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"5. ENOENT 错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -c \"ENOENT\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"6. 子代理错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"unknown.*subagent\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"7. Network Error:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"network.*error\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"8. aborted 错误:\"\nfor f in $(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -360 -type f); do\n  cat \"$f\" 2>/dev/null\ndone | grep -ci \"aborted\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_32440bd86c3c48d793849306","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 系统资源状态\necho \"=== 系统资源 ===\"\necho \"磁盘:\"\ndf -h / | tail -1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"内存:\"\nfree -m | head -2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"CPU 负载:\"\ncat /proc/loadavg\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Gateway 进程状态 ===\"\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | head -2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 最近活动 Session 数 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mmin -60 -type f | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== SWE-Agent-Node 迭代状态 ===\"\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/swe-agent-node/.iteration-state.json 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"(totalIterations|successCount|failureCount)\" | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":40612,"output":947,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772380801408}}
